'This is but the first part of the plan, [placeholder], but is the most important. You cannot fight an enemy that is simply too strong or too numerous. Our victory here must be decisive.'
Uruk emissaries from Isengard prowl Skrithûrz-ulíma, attempting to win over Moria Orcs as allies for Saruman.

The White Hand ambassadors can be found within Skrithûrz-ulíma, a Moria Orc-encampment north-west of the Orc-watch. \n\nYou should defeat White Hand ambassadors to prevent an alliance between Moria and Isengard.
You have helped to thwart an alliance between Moria Orcs and Isengard.
